<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=English_orthography&amp;action=edit&amp;section=22" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.all-about-spelling.com" class="external text" title="http://www.all-about-spelling.com" rel="nofollow">Teaching Spelling</a> - Information on teaching English spelling</li>
<li>Rules for English Spelling: <a href="http://www.kwiznet.com/p/takeQuiz.php?ChapterID=10015&amp;CurriculumID=26" class="external text" title="http://www.kwiznet.com/p/takeQuiz.php?ChapterID=10015&amp;CurriculumID=26" rel="nofollow">Adding Suffixes</a>, <a href="http://www.kwiznet.com/p/takeQuiz.php?ChapterID=10016&amp;CurriculumID=26" class="external text" title="http://www.kwiznet.com/p/takeQuiz.php?ChapterID=10016&amp;CurriculumID=26" rel="nofollow">QU Rule</a>, <a href="http://www.kwiznet.com/p/takeQuiz.php?ChapterID=10017&amp;CurriculumID=26" class="external text" title="http://www.kwiznet.com/p/takeQuiz.php?ChapterID=10017&amp;CurriculumID=26" rel="nofollow">i before e</a>, <a href="http://www.kwiznet.com/p/takeQuiz.php?ChapterID=10018&amp;CurriculumID=26" class="external text" title="http://www.kwiznet.com/p/takeQuiz.php?ChapterID=10018&amp;CurriculumID=26" rel="nofollow">Silent e</a>, <a href="http://www.kwiznet.com/p/takeQuiz.php?ChapterID=10021&amp;CurriculumID=26" class="external text" title="http://www.kwiznet.com/p/takeQuiz.php?ChapterID=10021&amp;CurriculumID=26" rel="nofollow">'er' vs. 'or'</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.espindle.org/whitepaper.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.espindle.org/whitepaper.pdf" rel="nofollow">White Paper</a> Research based Tutoring of English Spelling</li>
<li><a href="http://zompist.com/spell.html" class="external text" title="http://zompist.com/spell.html" rel="nofollow">Hou tu pranownse Inglish</a> describes rules which predict a word's pronunciation from its spelling with 85% accuracy</li>
<li><a href="http://www.thephonicspage.org/On%20Spelling/onspellinglinks.html" class="external text" title="http://www.thephonicspage.org/On%20Spelling/onspellinglinks.html" rel="nofollow">Free spelling information</a> and <a href="http://www.thephonicspage.org/On%20Spelling/spellinglessonsl.html" class="external text" title="http://www.thephonicspage.org/On%20Spelling/spellinglessonsl.html" rel="nofollow">Free spelling lessons in QuickTime movie format</a> at <a href="http://www.thephonicspage.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.thephonicspage.org/" rel="nofollow">The Phonics Page</a>.</li>
</ul>


